z
This will draw a "picture frame" around the edge of Vplot's standard
z
3 by 4 window. The central dotted line shows the exact edge of the
z
window. This should show JUST on the edge of your screen on 3 sides,
z
if you use "size=relative". This is a sensitive test of seeing whether
z
dev_xmin, dev_xmax, dev_ymin, and dev_ymax are correct!
z
If you use "size=absolute", the frame should have the given dimensions,
z
but the frame is not constrained to fit to the screen.
z

